STEP 1:
    - create a vite app "npm create vite@4" in the folder you want your app folder to be.
    - choose a project name, choose a framework "react, javascript"
    - install the dependencies manually "npm i"
    - delete the css files "index.css, App.css". we would create a new one
    - delete the code in "App.jsx" and use rafce to scafold a new component


STEP 2:
    - Setting Up ESlint "npm install eslint vite-plugin-eslint eslint-config-react-app --save-dev"
    - @.eslintrc.cjs add {"extends": "react-app"}
    - @vite.config.js we will add the eslint plugin
            import eslint from "vite-plugin-eslint"
            ...plugins: [react(), eslint()]
    